# parallel-issue-wave-execution — History

## v2.2.0 (2026-04-13)

**Changed by:** ProjectScylla batch-PR session Wave 2b/2c continuation
**Verification:** verified-ci

### What changed
- Added 4 new Failed Attempts rows (git rebase --no-edit, parallel PR conflict, auto-merge clearing, duplicate agent)
- Added Merge Conflict Resolution subsection to Verified Workflow
- Added Background Agent Coordination and Wave Completion Verification patterns to Results & Parameters
- Updated date, version, Verified On table

### Why
Continuation session surfaced non-obvious failure modes: `git rebase --no-edit` doesn't exist on this git version; auto-merge silently clears on force-push including rebase resolutions; parallel PRs on "different" issues can conflict when both add tests to a shared test file; background agents need checklist coordination to avoid duplicate work and wasted PRs.

