# Parallel Issue Wave Execution

## Overview

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Date | 2026-04-10 |
| Objective | Implement 20-35 issues per repo in parallel waves using myrmidon swarm agents, with pre-verification and CI-first strategy |
